description: Quiskee's Kitchen serves Burgers, Steak/Chicken Shawarma's (gyros), and Steak or Chicken Rice Bowls! All our meat is hand butchered, marinated, & char-grilled to perfection! We also have a marinated from scratch 3/4lb burger that is to die for! All our sauces are made from scratch and compliment our meats to create a very delightful culinary experience.Check us out and catch us rolling through the DFW!
name: Quiskee's Kitchen
